# Tyler ECF5 Vendor Artifacts

This directory contains vendor-provided Tyler ECF5 / EFM artifacts organized by version.

## Structure

- `versions/<version>/wsdl`  – WSDL definitions as provided by Tyler
- `versions/<version>/xsd`   – XML Schemas (XSD) as provided by Tyler
- `versions/<version>/docs`  – PDFs, DOCs, and other reference documentation
- `versions/<version>/notes` – Notes, provenance, and correspondence

## Current active artifacts

- **2025.2** – Generic / jurisdiction-neutral ECF5 / EFM 2025.2 artifacts.

GA/TX differences are handled at the configuration layer only and are **not** reflected in the WSDL/XSD themselves.
